f","tid":131920,"uid":15792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢d國家有乜撚野好去呀<br />\n仲要自己一個去<br />\n你咁都唔阻止個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實係大城市恐怖 其他小town 無問題的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點知？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我宜家仲係印度 第三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係男定女？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男 我哩到仲有幾個女 都係自己一個 同大量大陸人 根本唔使驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地幾個冇事就代表唔洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5245622f2d768501690e71bc021cf02d7bc526b5","tid":131920,"uid":15792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真答你<br />\n係香港打晒d防疫針，法國醫院有得搞<br />\n水就去到只可買樽裝<br />\n夜晚盡量少出門la<br />\n<br />\n利申，去過兩個禮拜冇任何事返黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個真 6點後唔好出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又話唔洗驚 冇問題<br />\n咁點解6點後唔好出街呀 你驚咩呀"},{"pid":"3c3949844c2d5e8faae7e84a26411adc6370182c","tid":131920,"uid":77057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真答你<br />\n係香港打晒d防疫針，法國醫院有得搞<br />\n水就去到只可買樽裝<br />\n夜晚盡量少出門la<br />\n<br />\n利申，去過兩個禮拜冇任何事返黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個真 6點後唔好出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n...夜晚出去先多野睇 成班後生唔返屋企 係咁吹水同捉住你影相抄牌"},{"pid":"2aac9e7599de42b594716401fc0501d6973cb246","tid":131920,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:49:42.000Z","msg":"一個女仔要痕到咩地步先會自己去印度旅行？"},{"pid":"f18d1f77becad76510a0e30fa30a86bb8fe8023e","tid":131920,"uid